The '''Overliege''', or '''Ukian Overliege''', was the [[King/Legends|monarch]] of [[Ukio/Legends|Ukio]]. During the onset of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], the title was held by an [[unidentified liege]], who welcomed [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Tyzen Xebec]] to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]. His rule came to an abrupt halt due to the turmoil caused by the conflict. As a result of the [[battle of Ukio]], he was ousted from his position as the planet decided to join the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederacy of Independent Systems]].

In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], the new Overliege was [[Topas dosLa]], who oversaw the transition of the planet as it seceded from the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. By [[5 ABY/Legends|5 ABY]], the Overliege was [[Gol dosLa]], but his son [[Tol dosLla]] served as his primary spokesman.

When [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo/Legends|Mitth'raw'nuruodo]] attacked Ukio in [[9 ABY/Legends|9 ABY]],<ref name="TLC">''[[The Last Command]]''</ref><ref name="TERC">''[[The Essential Reader's Companion]]''</ref> the Overliege surrendered the planet in the face of turbolaser fire that appeared to be capable of penetrating the planetary shields, although in fact it was an elaborate deception.<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|III|277|Ukio}}</ref>

